{"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/demon-form.webp","name":"Spell Effect: Demon Form (Dark Beast)","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule-feats.dzRnnjLp7HIedzTE]{Calamitous Form}'s <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.dKbv80rlAWVpz83C]{Demon Form}.</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>You corrupt yourself with sin, transforming into a demon battle form. While in this form, you gain the demon and fiend traits. You have hands in this battle form and can use manipulate actions. You can Dismiss the spell.</p>\n<p>You gain the following statistics and abilities regardless of the form that you choose:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AC = 20 + your level. Ignore your armor check's penalty and Speed reduction.</li>\n<li>30 temporary Hit Points, weakness 5 to cold iron, and weakness 5 to good.</li>\n<li>Darkvision.</li>\n<li>One or more attacks specific to the battle form you use. You're trained with them. Your attack modifier is +22, and you use the listed damage. These attacks are Strength based (for the purpose of the enfeebled condition, for example). If your attack modifier is higher for the given unarmed attack or weapon, you can use it instead.</li>\n<li>Athletics modifier of +23, unless your own modifier is higher.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You also gain specific abilities based on the type of demon you choose:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dark Beast</strong> Huge, Speed 30 feet;\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> horn or tusk (reach 15 feet), <strong>Damage</strong> 2d12+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil or chaotic;</li>\n<li><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> hoof (agile, reach 15 feet), <strong>Damage</strong> 2d8 bludgeoning plus 1d6 evil or chaotic;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.UNah0bxXxkcZjxO3]{Trample} <span class=\"pf2-icon\">3 </span>Large or smaller.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Secrets of Magic"},"rules":[{"hasHands":t