{"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/demon-form.webp","name":"Spell Effect: Demon Form (Demonic Monarch)","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule-feats.dzRnnjLp7HIedzTE]{Calamitous Form}'sÂ <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.dKbv80rlAWVpz83C]{Demon Form}</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>You corrupt yourself with sin, transforming into a demon battle form. While in this form, you gain the demon and fiend traits. You have hands in this battle form and can use manipulate actions. You can Dismiss the spell.</p>\n<p>You gain the following statistics and abilities regardless of the form that you choose:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AC = 20 + your level. Ignore your armor check's penalty and Speed reduction.</li>\n<li>30 temporary Hit Points, weakness 5 to cold iron, and weakness 5 to good.</li>\n<li>Darkvision.</li>\n<li>One or more attacks specific to the battle form you use. You're trained with them. Your attack modifier is +22, and you use the listed damage. These attacks are Strength based (for the purpose of the enfeebled condition, for example). If your attack modifier is higher for the given unarmed attack or weapon, you can use it instead.</li>\n<li>Athletics modifier of +23, unless your own modifier is higher.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You also gain specific abilities based on the type of demon you choose:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Demonic Monarch </strong>Large, Speed 25 feet;\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> horn or spear (reach 10 feet), <strong>Damage</strong> 2d8+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil or chaotic;</li>\n<li><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> hoof or tail, <strong>Damage</strong> 2d10 bludgeoning plus 1d6 evil or chaotic;</li>\n<li><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> claw or sword (agile), <strong>Damage</strong> 2d4 slashing plus 1d6 evil or chaotic;</li>\n<li>all Strikes deal 2d6 additional precision damage to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} creatures.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Secrets of Magic"},"rules":[{"hasHands":true,"key":"BattleForm","overrides":{"armorClass":{"modifier":"20 + @actor.level"},"senses":{"darkvision":{}},"size":"lg","skills":{"ath":{"modifier":23}},"speeds":{"land":25},"strikes":{"claw":{"ability":"str","baseType":"claw","category":"unarmed","damage":{"damageType":"slashing","dice":2,"die":"d4"},"modifier":22,"traits":["unarmed","agile"]},"sword":{"label":"Sword","group":"sword","ability":"str","baseType":"longsword","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/weapons/longsword.webp","category":"simple","damage":{"damageType":"slashing","dice":2,"die":"d4"},"modifier":22,"traits":["agile"]},"hoof":{"ability":"str","category":"unarmed","damage":{"damageType":"bludgeoning","dice":2,"die":"d10"},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unarmed-attacks/foot.webp","label":"PF2E.BattleForm.Attack.Hoof","modifier":22,"traits":["unarmed"]},"tail":{"ability":"str","category":"unarmed","damage":{"damageType":"bludgeoning","dice":2,"die":"d10"},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unarmed-attacks/tail.webp","label":"PF2E.BattleForm.Attack.Tail","modifier":22,"traits":["unarmed"]},"spear":{"ability":"str","baseType":"jaws","category":"simple","damage":{"damageType":"piercing","dice":2,"die":"d8","modifier":10},"group":"spear","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/weapons/spear.webp","label":"PF2E.Weapon.Base.spear","modifier":22,"traits":["reach-10"]},"horn":{"ability":"str","category":"unarmed","damage":{"damageType":"piercing","dice":2,"die":"d8","modifier":10},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unarmed-attacks/horn.webp","label":"PF2E.BattleForm.Attack.Horn","modifier":22,"traits":["reach-10","unarmed"]}},"tempHP":30,"traits":["demon","fiend"],"weaknesses":[{"type":"cold-iron","value":5},{"type":"good","value":5}]}},{"category":"precision","diceNumber":2,"dieSize":"d6","key":"DamageDice","predicate":["target:condition:flat-footed"],"selector":"strike-damage"},